short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome extension to get the HTML content of the current webpage.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Description:
This is a Chrome extension for extracting and displaying video content from the current webpage. Users can view a popup window containing a list of video source links by clicking the extension icon. Each list item has a "Visit" button that allows users to open the video link in a new tab directly.

Features:

Extracts all video content from the current webpage.
Displays the extracted video links in a list format in a popup window.
Provides a "Visit" button for each video source link to open the link in a new tab.
Adds a serial number to each video source link for easy identification by users.
How to Use:

Click on the extension icon in the browser toolbar.
View the list of video source links in the popup window.
Click the "Visit" button in the list to open the corresponding video link in a new tab.
Notes:

The extension only extracts links within the <video> tags.
If there are no <video> tags or <video> tags on the webpage, the popup window will be empty.
